description.content:
Develop Drupal website or fix and update, modules and themes Services!


About me:

I am Drupal Expert with good logical skill. During my 7 year's experience, I have worked over various types of tasks like Fronted/Backend Development, Custom Module/Theme development, E-commerce & marketplace integration, Search API & Solar integration, and many more.


Features of Gig:


  1. Complete design/development of a Drupal Website
  2. Fresh installation (7/8)
  3. Custom Development
  4. Maintenance / Site Backup
  5. Module or theme bug fixing
  6. Theme customization (like demo setting)
  7. Migration from old version to new version
  8. Migration from one server to another
  9. Update Modules and Upgrade Version
  10. Major frequent updates per release
  11. REST API etc.


I guarantee that website developed by me will be loading in browser in minimum second time.


CMS Expertise

    WordPress, Shopify, Magento, Joomla, PrestaShop, OpenCart, Wix and Drupal. 


Why me?

1) Professional work and swift response

2) Assuring satisfaction

3) Well-designed and planned workflow

4) support on project


Note: Please inbox me before placing your order.
